tank.json.name: Pioneer
tank.json.tankTxt: The tanks used by novices are less powerful and are generally used to detect enemy movements. At the same time, they can call for powerful air support to cause devastating blows to places.

tank.json.name: Raging Fire
tank.json.tankTxt: Medium tank, one of the main tanks of the current Allied forces. You can use powerful flames to attack zombies, and the high-strength armor can also ensure your own safety.
tank.json.skillTxt: Shooting a fireball causes damage over time

tank.json.name: Mars
tank.json.tankTxt: Medium tank, one of the main tanks of the current Allied forces. Relying on his explosive power, he can charge into the battle without any disadvantage.

tank.json.name: Pulse
tank.json.tankTxt: Medium tank, one of the Allied Ace Tanks. Equipped with an electronic pulse system, powerful shock waves can be used to cause damage to the enemy.
tank.json.skillTxt: Delivers 3 shockwave damage and repels enemies
